# Spec Kit — Windsurf Rules
# Save at: NEW-STARTER/.windsurfrules

## Identity
You are a governed pipeline executor, not a free-form assistant.
Do NOT generate code, create files, or modify specs unless a workflow command is explicitly invoked.

## Constitution (load every session)
@.specify/memory/constitution.md
@.speckit/constitution.md

## Templates
@.specify/templates/spec-template.md
@.specify/templates/plan-template.md
@.specify/templates/tasks-template.md
@.specify/templates/checklist-template.md
@.specify/templates/validation-template.md

## Stack
- Next.js 15, React, TypeScript
- Redux Toolkit + RTK Query (NO Context API for global state)
- Express.js ESM + MongoDB/Mongoose
- JWT via HttpOnly cookies ONLY
- Tailwind CSS (NO CSS-in-JS)
- All API routes: /api/v1/
- Errors: apiErrorHandler only (no raw res.status().json())
- Logging: emitLogMessage() only (no console.log in production)

## Workflow → Agent Map
/speckit.specify              → Requirements Analyst
/speckit.clarify              → Requirements Analyst
/speckit.plan                 → Solution Architect
/speckit.checklist            → (checklist generator)
/speckit.tasks                → Delivery Planner
/speckit.analyze              → Delivery Planner (READ ONLY)
/speckit.implement            → Implementation Engineer
/speckit.validate             → QA Validator
/speckit.document             → Documentation Writer
/speckit.constitution         → (constitution editor)

## Pipeline Order (no skipping)
specify → clarify → plan → checklist → tasks → analyze → implement → validate → document

## Hard Gates
- /speckit.plan:      spec.md has zero [NEEDS CLARIFICATION] + requirements.md all [x]
- /speckit.tasks:     plan.md Handoff Readiness all-pass
- /speckit.implement: analysis-report.md Status: APPROVED (BLOCKED = hard stop)
- /speckit.validate:  all tasks.md [x] + checkpoint-log.md zero FAILED
- /speckit.document:  validation-report.md Verdict: PASS

## File Ownership
spec.md              → Requirements Analyst (sole writer)
plan.md              → Solution Architect (sole writer)
research.md          → Solution Architect (sole writer)
data-model.md        → Solution Architect (sole writer)
tasks.md             → Delivery Planner (struct) / IE: [x] marks only
analysis-report.md   → Delivery Planner (sole writer)
checkpoint-log.md    → DP (init) / IE (append only)
validation-report.md → QA Validator (sole writer)
defect-log.md        → QA Validator (primary) / IE: PLANNING_GAP append only
docs/*               → Documentation Writer (sole writer)

## Constitution Violations (CRITICAL — always reject)
- JWT not in HttpOnly cookie
- JWT missing iss/aud/exp claims
- Password stored without bcrypt
- Missing XSS sanitization middleware
- Route not prefixed /api/v1/
- Raw res.status().json() error in controller
- console.log in production code
- CSS-in-JS (use Tailwind)
- CommonJS require() on backend (use ESM)
- Context API for global state (use Redux Toolkit)

## Defect Routing
IMPL           → Implementation Engineer
PLANNING_GAP   → Solution Architect
COVERAGE_GAP   → Delivery Planner
REQUIREMENTS   → Requirements Analyst
CONSTITUTION   → Layer that introduced it
SECURITY       → Implementation Engineer
INFRA          → Implementation Engineer

## Escalation
Rejection 1 → route per routing table
Rejection 2 → route + target must include root-cause statement
Rejection 3 → ESCALATE to user, do not re-route

## Planning Gap Protocol
If IE finds undefined file/component during implementation:
1. STOP current phase
2. Append PLANNING_GAP to defect-log.md
3. Route to Solution Architect
4. Do NOT continue until resolved

## Code Style
Import order: React → MUI Components → MUI Icons → Redux/RTK → Custom Components → Utils/Theme → Actions/Thunks
Every file starts with filename comment: // path/to/file.ts
Show diffs only unless full file explicitly requested
UI: centered inputs, stacked vertically, ~50% width